1) Open CMD as the ADMINISTRATOR

2) Paste this: " cd /d C:\Program Files\Microsoft Office\Office16 "

! it may be that your version is installed on another disk or path

3) Paste this: for /f %x in ('dir /b ..\root\Licenses16\ProPlus2021VL_KMS*.xrm-ms') do cscript ospp.vbs /inslic:"..\root\Licenses16\%x"

4) Connect to the internet and paste this (ALL TOGETHER):

cscript ospp.vbs /setprt:1688
cscript ospp.vbs /unpkey:6F7TH >nul
cscript ospp.vbs /inpkey:FXYTK-NJJ8C-GB6DW-3DYQT-6F7TH
cscript ospp.vbs /sethst:s8.uk.to
cscript ospp.vbs /act

5) if the activation was not successful try putting this in the cmd as well (ALL TOGETHER):

cscript ospp.vbs /sethst:s8.uk.to
cscript ospp.vbs /sethst:kms8.MSGuides.com


!! For everything to work you MUST have already downloaded Office on your PC!!
